    "By concentrating on minimising errors that could significantly impact patient care, we can align LLMs with clinical safety standards and regulations.",
    "To our knowledge, we have conducted the largest manual evaluation on the task of LLM clinical note generation to date.",
    "To implement our framework at scale we built CREOLA, an in-house platform, designed to enable clinicians to identify and label relevant hallucinations and omissions in clinical text and inform future experiments.",
